  "description": "Approval workflow gate for publication of soil nitrogen analysis manuscript from Quilima Vineyards Drought Mitigation Phase 2 research program",
  
  "document_metadata": {
    "manuscript_title": "Soil Nitrogen Dynamics in Organic Grain Rotation Systems: A Multi-Zone Analysis Across Two Harvest Cycles",
